3. Drop in main content area
4. Success notification appears
5. Spell card shows in character's grimoire

**Method 2 - Click to Add:**
1. Select character (left sidebar)
2. Hover over spell in right sidebar
3. Click blue "+" button
4. Same result as drag & drop

**Removing Spells:**
1. Hover over spell card in main area
2. Click red "×" button
3. Spell removed with confirmation notification

