## ✅ **Grimoire Auto-Refresh Fixed!**

I've implemented a refresh trigger mechanism that ensures the grimoire (main content area) updates automatically when spells are added or removed from a character.

### ** How the Fix Works:**

1. **Refresh Trigger State** - Added `grimoireRefreshTrigger` counter in App component
