   427			 * This endpoint deletes an existing Super Blog Clone.  The request must include APPNAME and PERSONA.
   428			 * The endpoint deletes the blog entirely and this action may not be undone.  Removes Wordpress installation
   429			 * from the server filesystem, the Wordpress database, as well as its entry from RFSB `blog` table.
   430			 */
