Next, I'd like to enhance the `Add New Character`, `Edit Character`, `Add New Spell`, and `Edit Spell` modal dialogs. The problem I want to address is, suppose a user is adding a new spell and has invested quite a bit of time in formatting the spell description, and then hits the Escape key by accident. All of their work is lost.

