irty,\n    markClean,\n    checkDirty: () => checkDirty(currentData)\n  }\n}"}","mcp_server_name":"","mcp_tool_name":""}},{"id":2,"type":0,"content":"Perfect! Let me implement the unsaved changes protection system. I'll start by creating a reusable hook for tracking dirty state, then a confirmation dialog component, and finally update all the form modals.

